Read the implementation spec at `.hanness/pages/page_06_ui_hud.page` and implement everything described.

Prerequisites: page_03 (GameScene) and page_04 (CardSprite) must be complete.

Steps:
1. Create `client/src/scenes/LobbyScene.js` with nickname input and 4 buttons.
2. Create `client/src/scenes/RoomScene.js` with create/join room buttons and code input.
3. Create `client/src/scenes/WaitingScene.js` with ready status display and countdown.
4. Create `client/src/ui/HUD.js` with my-stat panel, opponent panel, kingdom build button.
5. Wire HUD.refresh() into GameScene.update().
6. Implement kingdom build button activation (score >= 30 → active, else grayed).
7. Register all scenes in client/src/main.js Phaser config.

After implementing, verify each acceptance criterion listed at the bottom of the spec.
